---

<section class="hero container">
  <img src="/computer-gif-30fps.gif" class="hero__img" />

  <div class="hero__intro">
    <h1 class="hero__title">Hello,<br />I'm Fume ðŸ™‚</h1>

    <p class="hero__desc">
      I love building cool <strong>software</strong> on the web. I'm a
      <strong> Full-Stack Web / Game Developer</strong> on a mission to
      build interactive, and immersive experiences on the web through a
      combination of <strong>Code</strong>, <strong>Design</strong>,
      and <strong>Animation</strong>. I love learning, consistently
      iterating and experimenting with new technologies. Feel free to
      check out some of my projects and let me know if you like to
      work together.
    </p>

    <!-- <button class="hero__btn btn">Reach Out</button> -->
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    /* Typography */
    text-align: center;

    /* Layout */
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .hero__img {
    /* Box Model for Image */
    width: 18.75rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--clr-dutch-white);
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .hero__title {
    /* Typography  */
    color: var(--clr-dutch-white);
    font-size: var(--size-4xl);
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    line-height: 0.9;
  }

  .hero__desc {
    /* Box Model */
    max-width: 60ch; /* Max width is super useful because it allows for responsiveness
    It means the html element can reduce and increase in size but it cannot go beyond the maximum width.*/
    margin: 1em 0;

    /* Typography */
    font-size: var(--size-sm);
    color: var(--clr-slate600);
  }

  .hero__btn {
    /** Typography */
    font-size: var(--size-sm);
  }

  /* -------------------- Adding Responsiveness ------------------------ */
  /* MOBILE FIRST PRE-DEFINED MEDIA QUERIES */
  /* xs */
  @media (min-width: 475px) {
    .hero {
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .hero__img {
      width: 28rem;
    }
    .hero__title {
      font-size: var(--size-5xl);
    }
    .hero__desc {
      font-size: var(--size-base);
    }
    .hero__btn {
      font-size: var(--size-base);
    }
  }

  /* sm */
  /* @media (min-width: 640px) {} */

  /* md */
  /* @media (min-width: 768px) {} */

  /* lg */
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .hero {
      flex-direction: row-reverse;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .hero__img {
      flex: 1;
      width: 30rem;
    }

    .hero__intro {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .hero__title {
      text-align: left;
      font-size: var(--size-7xl);
    }

    .hero__desc {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      text-align: justify;
      font-size: var(--size-lg);
    }

    .hero__btn {
      font-size: var(--size-lg);
    }
  }

  /* xl */
  /* @media (min-width: 1280px) {} */

  /* 2xl */
  /* @media (min-width: 1536px) {} */
</style>
